node.text: Which color of the new @Roger_Dubuis Excalibur Spider Pirelli is your favorite? 🤔 The ingenious Quick Release System allow easy and quick interchangeability of all three components of the watch - from bezel, crown to strap, with a simple click. This reference is available with three color kits in red, white or blue to quickly and easily change the look and feel of your watch. Another cool feature is the strap which is made of winning motorsport tyre rubber from real races 🏁 #RogerDubuis #NoRulesOurGame #Pirelli
